The Team








THE TEAM

Angelo, Gordon including affiliates has over 420 employees, including more than 160 investment professionals. Many of our key professionals have worked together for more than a decade. Our reputation has helped us to attract and retain the highest-caliber employees, many of whom are principals in the firm. The firm has fully-staffed risk management, accounting, compliance and client service groups. Our research analysts specialize in a number of different but related investment strategies. We encourage communication among all analysts in an effort to meet the common goal of understanding the risks and rewards of each investment opportunity. We believe our greatest asset is the collaborative way in which the various disciplines work together. 



