PRIVATE EQUITY





PRIVATE EQUITY
PRIVATE EQUITY strategies




About Us
Angelo, Gordon's Private Equity Group manages over $1 billion in existing investments and committed capital. We focus on acquiring businesses and assets with strong management that have the potential for meaningful growth and value creation.
WHY WORK WITH US?
Large Firm Resources for Smaller and Middle Market Transactions
We bring substantial resources, a broad network of relationships and a wide range of experience to add value to our portfolio companies.	

Strong and deep relationships with financial partners (lenders, equity co-investors, etc.) and transaction advisors (legal, financial, operational, etc.)

Focused Approach with Experienced Personnel
Our team of veteran investment professionals and seasoned senior advisors has the ability to identify transactions where we can uniquely add value. Key relationships with senior advisors include:	

Public company CEOs Industry veterans Experienced investors

Management-centric Approach
We recognize that we are not operators. Accordingly, we seek to partner with world class management teams as value added contributors. Our mission is to complement the skill sets of our management teams with (i) Angelo Gordon resources, (ii) senior advisor experience and (iii) investment professional financial acumen.	

We offer our management partners compelling equity incentive programs Unlike the vast majority of our peers, we do not charge portfolio management or transaction fees

Proven Track Record of Success
Our focused approach and broad experience within our key industries has produced strong and quantifiable results.	

Our investment professionals have a long and distinguished track record within our core verticals We seek to generate returns through fundamental growth rather than financial engineering




